(1, 'Barbie Be a Fashion Designer Doll Dress Up Kit', 1, 349.99, 9, 'Design Your Own Barbie Doll Fashions With The Barbie Be A Fashion Designer Dress Up Kit\r\nKit Includes 5 Dresses To Design And Decorate With Ribbons, Bows, Glitter, And Other Fun Accessories\r\nCountry Of Origin : United States\r\nApply Ribbons, Bows, Glitter, And Other Fun Accessories\r\n', 'A variety of clothes available for you to choose!', 'Barbie1.jpeg'),
(2, 'Disney Princess DPR Shimmer Snow White', 1, 249.99, 15, 'Snow White has shimmery glitter eyes and her signature black hair to style. This gorgeous Princess is approximately 14 inches tall. Includes doll, removable dress, shoes and Tiara. Also look for the matching Snow White girl dress! (sold separately) Recommended for ages 3+', 'Disney Princess My Friend Snow White Doll 14 inch', 'SnowWhite.jpeg'),
(3, 'Marvel Ultimate Spider-man Titan Hero ', 4, 350, 12, 'The realistic figure has 4 joints, including head, arms, legs, and feet. The head, arms and feet can be rotated 360 degrees, and the legs can swing forward and backward. Flexible joints not only improve your child\'s hands-on ability, but also improve imagination.he figure is made of eco-friendly and high-quality PVC materials, which is ideal for use as interior decoration displays and collections.', 'Series Spider-man Figure, 12-Inch', 'S.jpeg'),
(4, 'Barbie Camper, Doll Playset with 50 Accessories', 1, 850, 5, 'Transform the colorful Barbie DreamCamper into a campsite play set with the push of a button -the top pops up, the side pops out and the back expands to create a play space more than 2 feet long\r\nThe open side becomes a pool with a water slide and stairs that fold out to really make a splash\r\nUse the interior to eat or sleep -pull up the two seats from the front cab to create chairs for the table or hook up the hammocks to let two sisters sleep under the stars\r\nTwo more beds mean Barbie doll and all of her sisters can hit the road together (dolls sold separately)', 'Includes Waterslide, 2 Hammocks, Canopy Bed & Fireplace, Dream Camper.\r\n', 'BarbieS.png'),
(5, 'Disney Frozen Toys, Singing Elsa Doll in Signature Clothing ', 1, 349.99, 5, 'Inspired by the beloved animated character, this Elsa doll sings her celebrated song from Disney\'s Frozen!\r\nKids can press a button and join in as the Elsa doll sings a 30-second clip from her signature song, in English: \"Let It Go.\"\r\nElsa doll wears her classic blue outfit from the first Disney Frozen movie, with removable soft cape.\r\nShe also has soft, brushable hair and an authentic braided hairstyle from the movie.', 'Sings ‚ÄúLet It Go‚Äù from The Disney Movie Frozen', 'Elsa.jpeg'),
(6, 'Adora Realistic Baby Doll All Star Toddler Doll', 1, 399.99, 8, 'Interactive doll: Makes 5 sounds when your child plays with her. She Cries, Coos, Giggles, Kisses Back & Says Momma\r\nReacts to play: Squeeze her hand and she‚Äôll cry. Pat her head to hear her coo. Tickle her tummy to hear sweet giggles. Kiss her cheek and she‚Äôll kiss you back. Pat her head and she‚Äôll call you Momma', '20 inch, Soft CuddleMe Vinyl, Brown Hair, Brown Eyes', 'TG.jpg'),
(7, 'Soft Body Interactive Baby Doll', 1, 349.99, 10, 'Realistic Newborn Baby Dolls - Your \"little parent\" will love to care for this perfectly cute baby doll. Dolly has a lot of cute details. Her Arms, Legs, head and face are made of vinyl with a body that is soft and huggable. Her talking, laughing and crying sound features help toddlers, boys and girls create an awareness of their own real life emotions.', 'Can Talk, Cry, Sing and Laugh - Makes Cute Gibberish Sounds', 'TalkingBoy.jpeg'),
(9, '4 Inch Purple Fairy', 4, 500, 13, 'ENESCO FIGURINE: from the Disney Traditions by Jim Shore Collection, titled \"Ecstatic Elf\"\r\nDESIGN: combines Jim Shore\'s unmistakable style of traditional themes and quilt patterns with classic and modern Disney characters!\r\nHAND-CRAFTED: from high-quality stone resin and hand-painted with intricate styling and attention to detail', 'Sitting and Reading a Book Statue Figurine, Blue', 'x.jpg'),
(10, 'TAMASHII NATIONS - Naruto Shippuden - Naruto Uzumaki', 4, 449.99, 8, 'Naruto Uzumaki, as seen in \"NARUTO: Shippuden,\" rejoins S.H.Figuarts with all new joint technology\r\n[Set Contents] Main Body, Three left and four right optional hands, Four optional expressions, Kunai, \"Rasengan\" effect, Crossed arm parts\r\nStands approximately 5.5\" tall', '15 inch Naruto Figurine', 'd.jpg'),
(11, 'DC Comics, 12-inch Batman Action Figure', 4, 350, 7, '12-INCH ACTION FIGURE: With 11 points of articulation, it‚Äôs easy to pose this 12-inch Batman action figure into a variety of dynamic action poses. Create your own Batman pretend play adventures!\r\nAUTHENTIC COMIC STYLING: This articulated action figure is highly detailed, featuring a cloth cape and comic styling that brings your favorite Batman toys to life!\r\nCOLLECT THEM ALL: Bring the excitement of Batman home! Add Batman, Nightwing, Red Hood, The Joker and more to your Batman toy figures & playsets collection (each sold separately)!\r\nFANS AND COLLECTORS: This Batman 12-inch collectible Action Figure is a must-have Batman toy for fans and Justice League collectors!', 'Kids Toys for Boys and Girls Ages 3 and Up', 'B.jpg'),
(12, 'Goku Figure Statues Figurine DBZ Super Saiyan ssj3 Collection', 4, 299.99, 15, 'Simple construction patterns ensure it will be an easy to build figure even for those who have never built a model kit before!This Goku Statue Is A Great Gift Idea For Kids ( girls ) In any occasion !', 'Goku Figure Statues Figurine DBZ Super Saiyan ssj3 Collection', 'Goku.jpeg'),
(13, 'Farm Animals Figurines Toys, 53PCS Realistic Plastic ', 4, 259.99, 23, 'CHILD FRIENDLY & HIGH QUALITY: Farm Animal figurines are made of high quality durable ABS materials which is Eco-Friendly. BOLZRA\'s #1 priority is child safety. Please note this is designed for baby children ages 3 and up.\r\nREALISTIC FARM ANIMALS: 14PCS unique non-repeating plastic farm animals with vibrant colors, 8 pcs unique 4-5 inch big farm animals and 6 pcs 2 inch mini farm animals. Including Cow, Goat, Sheep, Dog, Dairy cattle, Donkey, Horse, Hen, Rooster, Goose, Duck, Pig. All accessories are in the storage box.', 'Farm Playset with Fences Soil Puzzle Blocks', 'm.jpg'),
(14, 'Star Wars Galactic Action The Mandalorian & Grogu', 4, 189.99, 19, 'FIGURE AND ACCESSORY-ACTIVATED: Protect Grogu at all costs by snuggling him into The Mandalorian\'s satchel to hear them interact, then attach his jetpack to enjoy even more galactic sound FX\r\nADDITIONAL REMOVEABLE ACCESSORY: These Galactic Action The Mandalorian & Grogu toys also come with a blaster inspired by The Mandalorian\r\n15 SERIES-INSPIRED SOUNDS: Activate 15 different sounds and phrases inspired by The Mandalorian through multiple ways of play, including pressing the button on the bounty hunter\'s chest', '12-Inch-Scale Action Figures, Toys for Kids Ages 4 and Up', 'r.jpg'),
(15, 'Logic Roots Pet Me Multiplication and Division Game ', 3, 450, 17, 'HAVE FUN WITH MULTIPLICATION AND DIVISION: Pet Me is an exciting math board game. Kids go on a pet park adventure, feed dogs, cats and parrots, win hearts and adopt them. They will master multiplication and division facts along the way. A very cool and fun game that builds mental math skills.\r\nMULTIPLE SKILL LEVELS AND 4X MORE PRACTICE - It has a host of engaging levels with math integrated in each step. Perfect for kids between the ages of 5 to 9 (grade 1 and up) and aligned with elementary school education. Beginners level and adaptable rules make it suitable for younger players too.', 'Fun Math Board Game for 5 - 9 Year Olds', 's.jpg'),
(16, 'Chutes and Ladders Board Game', 3, 250.99, 9, 'Ages:4 and up, Players:2 to 4\r\nFun without Words: ‚ÄòChutes and Ladders‚Äô is simple and easy to play, with no reading required. Be First to land on the 100 spot and win the game\r\nUP THE LADDERS AND DOWN THE CHUTES: Land on good deeds and climb ladders toward the winning spot. Land on bad deeds and ride the chutes back down\r\nTEACHES BASIC SKILLS: Great for kids who are learning to count, this game encourages basic addition skills', 'An exciting Up and Down game for children', 'q.jpg'),
(17, 'Monopoly Junior Dinosaur Edition Board Game', 3, 1299.99, 5, 'KIDS MONOPOLY GAME: DINOSAUR EDITION: In this Monopoly Junior board game, kids can imagine a world in which they come face-to-face with different kinds of dinosaurs and feed them leafy banknotes. Family board games everyone will love.\r\nFUN GAME FOR KIDS: Players can imagine making friends with the dino toys by feeding them. The Brontosaurus and Iguanadon are pretty affordable, but it\'s going to cost a lot to feed the Gigantosaurus. One of the funnest childrens games to add to the collection of dinosaur toys for kids.\r\nDINOSAUR NAMES: The gameboard spaces feature phonetic spellings of different kinds of dinosaurs so caregivers can help kids practice saying different dinosaur names', 'Kids Board Games, Fun Dinosaur Toys, Dinosaur Board Game for 2-4 players', 'e.jpg'),
(18, 'Travofun 2 in 1 Board Games for Kids Checkers Sets Board Games for Kids  ', 3, 479.99, 4, 'Checkers & Tic-Tac-Toe Children Board Games - BST SHIER is bringing fun and exciting 3-fold travel toys which include Eva checkers board game for kids and Tic-tac-toe game for kids 3-10 years to enjoy while traveling or as group activity. Checkers printed on EVA material & paper and foldable to fit in small backpack. Easy To Store, Light Weight, & Uniquely Designed - BST SHIER checkers & tic tac toe outdoor game opens just like a book and its simple 3-fold design makes it easy for children to carry anywhere.', 'AxcessAbles Isolation Pads, Audio Cables and eStudioStar Polishing', 'l.jpg'),
(19, 'NEILDEN Disney Frozen Puzzles in a Metal Box 60 Piece Jigsaw Puzzle for Kids', 2, 449.99, 9, 'The pieces of Frozen jigsaw puzzles are made of nontoxic and odorless material which are sturdy enough and do not tear easily so good for children. The die-cuts of kids puzzles are smooth, allowing for easy assembly\r\nClassic Storage Box: Frozen jigsaw puzzle comes with a metal box which is quite convenient to store and takes for travel. The pieces will not be lost as well . Kids enjoy doing puzzles and form good habits of integrating things', 'Puzzle for Kids Ages 3+ for Children Learning Educational Puzzles Toys (Snowman) Authorized by Disney', 'k.png'),
(20, 'Puzzles for Kids Ages 4-8 60 Pieces Jigsaw Puzzles for Boys and Girls', 2, 449.99, 24, '1-Package Containt: 60 pieces puzzles and a 1:1 reference poster that will help chirldren to finish the puzzle. One metal box help storage every pieces conveniently.\r\n2-Puzzle Size: The jigsaw puzzle has 60 pieces, it\'s perfect for children ages 4-8 years old. The size of every single piece:1.5\'*1\'. Finished size: 9.5\'*6\'.Metal box size: 3.25\'*5.25\'.\r\n3-High Quality: Every piece is unique, complete cutting and fits perfectly. We produce our jigsaw puzzle toys of 100% safe high-quality materials & FSC compliant wood that meet Safety Standards', 'Puzzles for Kids Ages 4-8 60 Pieces Jigsaw Puzzles for Boys and Girls Educational Learning Puzzles in Metal Box Thomas ', 'v.jpg'),
(21, 'LELEMON Disney Car Jigsaw Puzzles in a Metal Box 60 Pieces Lightning McQueen', 2, 449.99, 5, 'üöí60 Pieces Puzzles for Kidsüöí -- Every Package Includes Puzzle Pieces, a Tin Box, An Original Picture. Sturdy Boxes Are Perfect For Gifting, Stacking And Storage. Puzzles Can Bring Entertainment And Fun Time To Everyone! and Help Children Gain A Sense Of Accomplishment In The Puzzle Process.', 'McQueen Jigsaw Puzzle for Kids Ages 4-8 Children Learning Educational Puzzles Toys', 'u.png'),
(25, 'LELEMON Disney Mickey Mouse Puzzle for Kids Ages 4-8 in a Metal Box 100 Piece ', 2, 549.99, 5, 'Puzzles for Kids: LELEMON Disney Mickey Mouse 100 Pieces Puzzles come in a tin box for easy storage and not easy to lose puzzle pieces. Playing puzzles can stimulate children\'s reasoning and thinking skills, improve hand-eye coordination, and improve children\'s resistance to frustration.\r\nHigh Quality Material: Jigsaw puzzles are made of non-toxic and odorless material. The surface pattern is vivid and clear, smooth and easy to clean. We use precision cutting techniques to ensure that each puzzle piece fits perfectly, which is sturdy and secure.\r\nBenefits of Playing Puzzles: Puzzles make children smarter, develop children\'s observation, patience and concentration, and help children build self-confidence. In the learning of puzzles, children will gradually develop various strategies and learn to sort out the clues to complete the puzzle from the chaos.', 'For Kids Ages 4-8 in a Metal Box 100 Piece Learning Educational Puzzles for Children Girls and Boys(Mickey & Minnie)', 'i.jpg'),
(26, 'Mudpuppy Animals of The World Puzzle Sticks', 2, 1000, 15, '6 PUZZLES IN ONE ‚Äì The Animals of the World Puzzle Sticks from Mudpuppy includes 24 double-sided puzzle sticks that create six unique eight-piece puzzles!\r\nCOLORFUL DESIGNS ‚Äì This is a unique and easy puzzle for toddlers and children Sort the sticks by background colors, then use the included tray to arrange the sticks in the correct order to reveal a colorful penguin, whale, red panda, turtle, koala and lion', '24 Double-Sided Sticks Create 6 Different Puzzles ‚Äì Unique Animal Puzzles for Kids Ages 3-6 ‚Äì Puzzle Tray and Drawer Box Included, Multicolor', 'h.jpg'),
(27, 'Lego Technic Bugatti Chiron', 5, 4500, 5, 'The perfect gift for car lovers and future engineers! Build and experience a quintessential collectible sports car ‚Äì the LEGO Technic Bugatti Chiron! Developed in partnership with Bugatti Automobiles S.A.S, this is a faithful recreation of the real car. You can now answer the question: \"What colour is your Bugatti?\".', '42083 Race Car Building Kit and Engineering Toy, Adult Collectible Sports Car with Scale Model Engine (3599 Pieces)', 'bugatti.png'),
(28, 'Lego Star Wars X-Wing Fighter', 5, 3500, 5, 'Features a LEGO brick-built version of Luke Skywalker‚Äôs iconic toy X-wing Fighter to recreate scenes from the classic Star Wars trilogy. The X-wing features an opening LEGO minifigure cockpit, space for R2-D2 droid and wings that can be switched to attack position with a button\r\nThe X-wing buildable toy also features retractable landing gear and 2 spring-loaded shooters, plus an R2-D2 LEGO droid figure to fit in\r\nIncludes Luke Skywalker, Princess Leia and General Dodonna LEGO Star Wars minifigures with weapons including Luke‚Äôs lightsaber\r\nThis set comes with step-by-step, illustrated instructions so even first time young builders can build with Jedi-like confidence\r\nThis LEGO Star Wars X-wing building toy makes a super birthday present or Christmas gift for 9 plus year old boys and girls', '75301 Building Toy, Gifts for Kids, Boys & Girls with Princess Leia Minifigure and R2-D2 Droid Figure', 'LegoStarWars.png'),
(29, 'LEGO Creator 3 in 1 Exotic Parrot to Frog to Fish ', 5, 1500, 3, 'This LEGO Creator 3in1 animal toy set features 3 animals for kids 7+ years old: a parrot toy perched on a branch, a playful frog and a toy fish\r\nThe toy parrot is richly colored and comes with jointed parts that allow it to rotate its body on the branch and move its wings and tail\r\nThe parrot can be rebuilt into a toy frog with posable legs or into a LEGO fish with movable fins and a seabed for creative adventures\r\nKids can choose their building adventure with 3 LEGO Creator animal figures or fire up their imagination and create a new animal with the bricks\r\nWith details such as the parrot\'s branch covered in flowers, this building toy set will look awesome on display in kids\' rooms when play is over\r\nThe easy-to-follow picture guide makes construction easy and fun, plus digital building instructions can also be found in the LEGO Builder app\r\nThis set makes a great Easter basket stuffer for girls and boys\r\nThe parrot toy measures over 22 cm (8.5 in.) high, 11 cm (4 in.) long and 12 cm (4.5 in.) wide. Contains 253 pieces', 'Frog to Fish 31136 Animal Figures Building Toy, Creative Toys and Easter Gift for Kids Ages 7 and up', 'LegoParrot.png'),
(30, 'Brickyard Building Blocks', 5, 1200, 12, 'More Pieces Than Other Sets Of Similar Price - We give you 20% more blocks than other similar sets. It is the most value set on Amazon in terms of versatility and number of pieces\r\nGreater Variety Of Blocks - While other sets contain only 2 different shapes of blocks (square and rectangular), Brickyard Large Building Blocks includes 9 different block shapes (including blocks with printed eyes), allowing for greater versatility, flexibility, and more ways to build\r\nBonus! Includes Building Ideas - At last, a building block set that includes a colorful building ideas guide in every box. This set contains enough building blocks to build 23 different figures at the same time\r\nCompatible With Duplo - Works with all major brands. Because we\'re so confident you\'ll love this 100% compatible building block set, it\'s backed by our No-Hassle Satisfaction Guarantee. If you don\'t love it for any reason, you can return it for a full refund\r\nMeets All U.S. Toy Safety Standards - We manufacture our products using only child-friendly materials and regularly conduct rigorous lab tests to make sure your kids are 100% safe from harmful chemicals. Your kid\'s safety is our #1 priority!', ' 177 Pieces Large Building Block Toys for Children Ages 1.5 - 5, Bulk Block Set, Compatible with Duplo (177 pcs)', 'LegoBB.png'),
(31, 'LEGO City Farmers Market Van ', 5, 2000, 5, 'Children with a passion for shop play will love the LEGO City Farmers Market Van (60345), packed with inspiring details and functions for hours of imaginative play\r\nAll kids need to build a mobile farm shop and veggie patch, with lots of play-inspiring features, plus 3 minifigures, including a LEGO City TV character, and a rabbit figure\r\nThe Farmers Market Van comes with a serving window, opening side doors, rear doors and a minifigure cab, while the veggie patch features a fun carrot-growing function\r\nThe Farmers Market Van playset can be given as a holiday, birthday or any-other-day gift for boys and girls aged 5 and up\r\nDimensions ‚Äì When built, the LEGO City Farmers Market Van measures over 4 in. (10 cm) high, 10 in. (25 cm) long and 6.5 in. (17 cm) wide', '60345 Building Toy Set for Kids, Boys, and Girls Ages 5+ Mobile Farm Shop Playset with 3 Minifigures (310 Pieces)', 'LegoCity.png'),
(32, 'LEGO Marvel I am Groot!', 5, 499.99, 15, 'Movable Baby Groot ‚Äì The LEGO Marvel I am Groot (76217) build-and-play model is easy to position and pose\r\nIconic Marvel character ‚Äì Kids build their own Baby Groot, from Marvel Studios‚Äô Guardians of the Galaxy Vol. 2. The set also includes a pretend cassette tape and display nameplate\r\nRecreate dance moves ‚Äì The buildable model is easy to position and pose, and there‚Äôs even a pretend cassette tape included for make-believe music\r\nGift for kids ‚Äì A special birthday, holiday or any-day treat for kids aged 10 and up who are fans of Marvel Studios‚Äô Guardians of the Galaxy movies and the super cute Baby Groot\r\nBuild, play and display ‚Äì The highly posable model stands over 10.5 in. (26 cm) tall and comes with a cassette and a nameplate.', '76217 Building Toy Set for Kids, Boys, and Girls Ages 10+ (476 Pieces)', 'LegoGroot.png'),
(33, 'LELEMON 100 Pieces Spiderman Jigsaw Puzzles', 2, 549.99, 6, 'üéÆPuzzles for KidsüéÆ-- The Jigsaw Puzzles Come with A Tin Box, Convenient to Storage And Not Easy to Lose Puzzles Piece.Many Kids Like to Make Jigsaw Puzzles, And Through Puzzle Learning, Kids Will Gradually Develop Various Strategies , And Learning to Sort Out The Clues of Completing The Puzzle from The Chaos Can Help Kid Improve Their Problem-solving Skills.\r\nüéÆHigh Quality MaterialüéÆ-- The Puzzle Are Made of Nontoxic And Tasteless Material,Vibrant and Clear Surface,Smooth and Easy to Clean.and We Using A Precision Cutting Technique That Assures Every Piece Will Fit Perfectly,Sturdy and Safe.\r\nüéÆSkills DevelopmentüéÆ -- The Puzzles Will Offer Various of Education Opportunities for Kids,exercise Children\'s Thinking And Logic Skills,develop Operational And Patient Skills.and The Vibrant Colors Attract Children\'s Attention And Are Easily Accepted And Loved By Them.\r\n\r\n', 'In a Metal Box for Kids Age for 4-8 Boys Girls Toy Puzzles Children Learning Educational Puzzles Toys', 'Spidermanpuzzle.png'),
(34, 'Slot Car Race Track Sets', 6, 850, 6, 'Realistic Racing Track: Our slot car race track sets simulates a variety of racing tracks, including simple straight track, S-shaped track, circular track and exciting double-layer overpass track. Bring the coolest racing experience to the racers. At the same time, our race track has an automatic lap counting function, which can record the status of the race in real time, allowing the racers to concentrate on the race.\r\nTwice the Fun for Two Players: Our race car track for boys age 4-7 8-12 is car toy for two racers, it comes with four slot cars, two durable remote controls (tested over 10,000 times). This is not just a friendship toy, but also a family toy, you can compete with your child, a great alternative to video games.\r\nExtra Long Tracks for Easy Installation: The slot car track is 18.4 ft long, which is longer than most other products, and has a better system to lock into place and easy to assemble. In order to keep the car on the track better, we have enhanced the magnetism, but it is also important to control the speed, remember to slow down when turning. In addition, we also prepare extra brushes on the bottom of the car for you, which you can replace at any time.\r\nExciting High-Speed Racing: Our race car can reach a speed of about 300-370 mph on the electric race track, and you can fully feel the power and speed of the racing car in remote control racing. Plus, our kids race track set has two power modes, electric or 6xAA battery(not included), so your kids can experience the fun of racing at home or on the go.', ' with 4 High-Speed Slot Cars, Battery or Electric Race Car Track for Boys and Kids, Dual Racing Game Lap Counter Circular Overpass Track, Gifts Toys for Boys Kids Age 6 7 8-12', 'Hotwheel.png'),
(35, 'Fisher-Price Pretend Laptop', 6, 799.99, 4, 'Pretend laptop computer activity toy with multi-color lights and 55+ songs, sounds and phrases\r\n3 Smart Stages learning levels teach the alphabet, colors, counting, greetings, and Spanish words\r\nNumber and letter keyboard buttons, screen slider, and roller help develop fine motor skills, plus mirror and light-up \"touchpad\" help foster baby\'s visual skills\r\nHinged screen folds like a real laptop for storage or take-along play\r\nFor infants and toddlers ages 6-36 months\r\n', 'Learning Toy for Baby and Toddler with Light Music and Smart Stages Educational Content, Laugh & Learn', 'LaptopToy.png'),
(36, 'Remote Control Robot Dog', 6, 6500, 4, 'üê∂„ÄêInteractive Robot Dog„ÄëThis clever remote control puppy dog could perform a different dance with different music, and your baby will enjoy the pleasure of these actions. When your child touches the robotic dog\'s jaw, it will respond with a sound on the ground. When the eyes of the RC robot dog toy are bright, they are in the shape of a heart and emit a faint yellow light, which makes you feel very warm.\r\n‚ù§Ô∏è„ÄêMultifunctional robot dog toy„ÄëYou only need to use the remote control to make the smart robot dog do many actions, forward, backward, turn left, turn right, handstand, sit down, act like a spoiled child, push up, sing, dance, etc. Fun and fun bionic action, easy to achieve with one click that is like a real puppy to accompany your children. It is not only easy for kids to interact with this robot toy, but can help kids exercise finger flexibility and auditory discrimination.\r\nüî•„ÄêIntelligent Programmable RC Dog„ÄëTo inspire the imagination, programming the remote control robot dog to perform different actions is available. press multiple desired action buttons, up to 100 actions can be programmed, and after completion, multiple actions can be realized continuously show. let the robot do different actions, and let your child learn the easiest programming.\r\nüå∏„ÄêHigh Quality and Safe Material„ÄëThe smart robot toy is made of non-toxic ABS plastic, BPA-free, with smooth rounded edges, no sharp corners, and a sturdy design that will not break easily, totally safe for kids. The robot dog toy has a built-in rechargeable battery with 3.7V 600mAh (included). Please note: The remote control needs 2 AAA batteries to operate.', 'For Boys Girls Age 3 4 5+, Programmable Interactive & Smart Dancing Walking RC Robot Dog Toys with Touch Function, Voice Control, Electronic Dog Pets Toys', 'Dog.png'),
(37, 'First Act Discovery Disney Princess Electronic Keyboard', 6, 450, 10, 'MAKE MUSIC Let your little musician‚Äôs creativity soar with the First Act Disney Princess Keyboard!\r\nRECORD THEIR SONGS Record and playback the creative tunes your little one creates!\r\nEDUCATIONAL MUSICAL TOYS The First Act Princess Keyboard is great for developing their motor skills!\r\nPLAY ALONG The included sounds and rhythms will build up their musical creations!\r\nDISCOVER FIRST ACT First Act provides fun, vibrant, easy-to-use instruments for tiny beginners!', '22 Inch - 37 Keys ‚Äì Make Real Music, Sized for Kids - Record, Playback, Volume Control - Musical Instruments for Toddlers and Kids', 'Piano.png'),
